reviewText: This program was great, if you love Timon and Pumba from the Lion King you will no doubt love their own series.  Its too bad no one is airing this show now, its entertaining and great fun.
This was part of a collection for our son.  The condition was acceptable, and was shipped in a timely fashion.  It is a great way to add to collections, without having to spend a lot of money.

Contains "The Law of the Jungle" (from ep. 10), "Uganda Be an Elephant" (from ep. 5) and "Be More Pacific" (from ep. 11).

This is the fifth volume in the series. The Editorial Reviews is incorrect and is actually the content from Vol. 2: Grub's On. But despite that I recommend this.
